Nigeria National League side, Madiba FC will unveil their new players and kits next week. The unveiling ceremony will hold in Lagos. The modest club will be making their maiden appearance in the Nigeria National League this season. Madiba FC secured promotion to NNL from the Nationwide League last season and also won the Super 8 tournament. Madiba FC is in Southern Conference Group B3 alongside Ikorodu United FC, Ekiti United FC, Abeokuta Stormers FC, and FC Ebedei. The Lagos club will host Ekiti United in their opening game of the season at the Mobolaji Johnson Arena on March 19.